						<p>On a slab set up before the temple of Rāmaliṅgēśvara.</p>						

						<p>Velanāṇḍu: Kulōttuṅga-Rājendrachōḍaya.</p>						

						<p>This is dated Śaka 1093 <hi rend="italic">(Rāma-nidhi-vyōma-rāja),</hi> Khara, Uttarāyaṇa.</p>						

						<p>Records the gift of land for burning a perpetual lamp at Siripuram by Bollana of Doṇḍipāla<hi rend="italic">gōtra.</hi></p>						

